{"id":50358,"type":4,"name":"Battlefield 1942","name_cn":"战地1942","date":"2002-09-10","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/21/74/50358_Qla7K.jpg","rating":{"rank":1733,"total":94,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":4,"6":14,"7":31,"8":27,"9":13,"10":5},"score":7.5},"summary":"《战地1942》（Battlefield 1942，BF1942）是一款背景在第二次世界大战的第一人称射击游戏，由Digital Illusions CE（DICE）开发，并由美国艺电于2002年发布。游戏具有对抗电脑的单人模式和多人在线联机。\r\n游戏中，玩家可以选择五种兵种：侦查兵、突击兵、反坦克兵、医护兵和工兵。玩家同时可以使用各式二战时期的载具，包括坦克、战斗机、轰炸机、驱逐舰、火炮、防御设施、装甲运兵车和防空武器等。每场战斗都发生在著名的二战战场，包括太平洋、东欧、西欧和北非四个战区。游戏中两大对抗势力为同盟国与轴心国，但国家随着地图地点而改变，在太平洋战区中，同盟国为美国而轴心国为日本；在东欧、西欧、北非战区中，同盟国分别为苏联、美国和英国，而轴心国皆为德国。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>战地1942</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/18591\">EA DICE</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/13930\">Electronic Arts</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>Windows</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Mac</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>FPS</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Refractor Engine</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人/多人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2002-09-10</li><li><span>制作公司: </span>Digital Illusions CE</li><li><span>发行公司: </span>EA (Win)</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">发行公司: </span>Aspyr Media (Mac)</li>","collection":{"on_hold":6,"dropped":3,"wish":9,"collect":131,"doing":0},"tags":[{"name":"FPS","count":26},{"name":"PC","count":21},{"name":"DICE","count":14},{"name":"EA","count":11},{"name":"战地","count":7},{"name":"BF","count":6},{"name":"老游戏","count":5},{"name":"2002","count":4},{"name":"战争","count":4},{"name":"本地多人","count":2},{"name":"历史","count":2},{"name":"瑞典","count":1},{"name":"STEAM","count":1},{"name":"galgame","count":1},{"name":"神作","count":1},{"name":"GAL","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"crt":[{"id":15433,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/9e/22/15433_crt_qcrPC.jpg","name":"Großdeutsches Reich","desc":"客串"}],"staff":[{"id":13930,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/ed/80/13930_prsn_10ahO.jpg","name":"Electronic Arts","desc":"发行"},{"id":18591,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200